{"tid":650771,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"執咗個Playlist，入嚟聽吓香港有乜新歌？ (2018年17週)","createTime":"2018-05-02T15:27:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-06T08:29:11.000Z","uid":184592,"like":49,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"46968b19b34dc7878c6b8945afd6c9529886c52b","tid":650771,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:27:49.000Z","msg":"因為香港人已經唔睇《勁歌金曲》、少聽咗收音機、旺角CD街舖已滅絶，所以小弟第一次特登執個playlist方便大家知道香港有乜新歌，礙於私人時間有限，只可以跟住903歌曲排行榜去執出嚟，希望大家每個星期上住連登都可以聽歌：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLKXvY9gpxoBOicMeP1tGDsvZ8M6-_04lt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLKXvY9gpxoBOicMeP1tGDsvZ8M6-_04lt&d=LIBfEwBbbbuceM9MXPAJA3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ff9ad44a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLKXvY9gpxoBOicMeP1tGDsvZ8M6-_04lt</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2018年17週上榜歌曲頭五位</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">演員的自我修養 / 許廷鏗<br />\n橙海 / Supper Moment<br />\n城市當代配樂團/ RubberBand\t<br />\nYeah / 林二汶<br />\n理想家 / 盧冠廷</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">有冇邊首歌你哋覺得有驚喜呢？</div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*****<br />\n呢個計劃繼續與否視乎大家反應，小弟希望盡小小力守護粵語文化，同埋俾大家知道仲有本土音樂人喺努力緊。如果大家對歌曲或本計劃有任何意見，歡迎留言討論。（暫時做住youtube playlist先，未研究點整聽歌app playlist，btw 邊個app多人用又多廣東歌？）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n※回覆勿quote全帖※"},{"pid":"5c0610836d36e9130a7f7ffe5e796dab58245d29","tid":650771,"uid":28832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"28610f456b9f4dfe3ee26026575910d86408a200","tid":650771,"uid":184592,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:31:47.000Z","msg":"我自己幾鍾意「演員的自我修養 / 許廷鏗」嘅英倫風，令我諗起Radiohead &quot;High and Dry&quot;<br />\n「城市當代配樂團/ RubberBand」有啲Gospel 感<br />\n如果頒叱吒男歌手獎俾 盧冠廷，盧冠廷會唔會攞獎呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3507d6c0271c6f9eb55d28046870c47fe828824","tid":650771,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c0610836d36e9130a7f7ffe5e796dab58245d29","tid":650771,"uid":28832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:29:39.000Z","msg":"G持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:32:09.000Z","msg":"多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7863a1c9f32eabd853a8c884b266a4e0a547a4","tid":650771,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53428df4958ad357494b472182f12682c4999ed2","tid":650771,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:52:04.000Z","msg":"太夜無人聽歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dd21652c997d28b895278fe10e08161366d0f8","tid":650771,"uid":4206,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:56:11.000Z","msg":"希望樓主可以keep住做，費事到年尾啲頒獎禮又有人走出嚟話一首都未聽過，廣東歌已死呢啲說話"},{"pid":"63ce2894889e3f69f944074047ca03449be479c6","tid":650771,"uid":149487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T15:57:10.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n真係聽少左好多廣東歌"},{"pid":"4b56635a7e072b8ddae905474f6c0f7ca63f3a96","tid":650771,"uid":42848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"加油 keep住做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c7f1fb5b662eda98ec49d09e0534a4e3747e19d","tid":650771,"uid":3189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T17:13:02.000Z","msg":"其實連登有呢D都好<br />\n以前都成日上cm論壇睇下有咩新派台歌"},{"pid":"0dc771994a186fceec1d8ccb4d7104fdb30e5c64","tid":650771,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime