<br />\n我會盡量講心水，但視野有限，大家有咩心水都可以傾"},{"pid":"cb158bb47a61fa98b4e8a0db49c0b1adb26d3872","tid":650771,"uid":184592,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"220af96085423bb78d6ea0e57b7e694f867a8be8","tid":650771,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"電台plug d歌9成唔岩聽，<br />\n廣東歌新歌好似賣少見少，<br />\n我聽黎聽去都係聽舊歌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:28:11.000Z","msg":"試下聽，我係前排病咗長期留喺屋企先開903，一開之下發覺原來仲有有心人製作好歌，所以產生搞呢個計劃嘅念頭，我覺得用心製作而冇人知，好浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前排好歌有鄧小巧《和好》"},{"pid":"a78a1ce18504e6247489f2d7d890b70c1e54de43","tid":650771,"uid":135265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:29:55.000Z","msg":"幫你推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec372fe63768281caaa0ab2f2de9ecfd497d982","tid":650771,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:58:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"699a28e14f8054d00375391d48ec04183bc3dd40","tid":650771,"uid":184592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T01:35:52.000Z","msg":"返工推一推"},{"pid":"9bbd36cc5d1e977a4e782efc3986ed0521fac5bc","tid":650771,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb158bb47a61fa98b4e8a0db49c0b1adb26d3872","tid":650771,"uid":184592,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"220af96085423bb78d6ea0e57b7e694f867a8be8","tid":650771,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"電台plug d歌9成唔岩聽，<br />\n廣東歌新歌好似賣少見少，<br />\n我聽黎聽去都係聽舊歌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T23:28:11.000Z","msg":"試下聽，我係前排病咗長期留喺屋企先開903，一開之下發覺原來仲有有心人製作好歌，所以產生搞呢個計劃嘅念頭，我覺得用心製作而冇人知，好浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前排好歌有鄧小巧《和好》"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T02:11:16.000Z","msg":"樓主好有心，聽完你個playlist，<br />\n可能我口味較偏，暫時只係得林二汶同盧冠廷岩聽<br />\n<br />\n另外，樓主有冇聽過胡琳 4月份出個隻新碟？D歌唔錯 （好似Youtube未